                                </div>
                                                          </div>
                                                                                            <p style="margin-bottom:16px"><strong><a href="https://www.jewishbookcouncil.org/edith-bruck">Edith Bruck</a></strong> is a transnational Italian writer and the author of two dozen novels, short-story collections, books of poetry, and works of nonfiction. Born in Hungary in 1931, she has been publishing works of literature in Italian since 1959, five years after permanently settling in Italy.</p>

